INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "The Practical Guide to Oil Painting Techniques and Materials",	"The practical guide to oil painting techniques and materials is a complete video guide covering the practical and technical knowledge needed for those who want to explore the infinite potential of oil painting.");
INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "The Art of Twitter: Build a Business That Makes You $100/Day",	"The Art of Twitter is a business guide that will teach you how to grow a Twitter account from scratch (from 0 to 10000+ followers) and MONETIZE it to make $100+ every single day.");
INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "Bundle: Writing An Interpreter And Compiler In Go",	"We start with zero lines of code in the first book and up with a fully-working interpreter for the Monkey programming language, including the lexer, the parser, the AST and object system. Fully tested and runnable.");
INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "Was ist Merch Research & Strategy?",	"Merch Research & Strategy Abo ist ein monatliches Abonnement für alle deutschsprachigen Merch und Print-on-Demand Verkäufer. 2-3x im Monat erhalten alle Abonnenten einen ausführlichen Research Guide oder Strategie Guide, der sie bei ihrem täglichen Geschäft unterstützt. Primärer Fokus ist nach wie vor der US-amerikanische Markt, weil dort das Umsatzpotential am größten ist.");
INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "Holandés Errante: juego interactivo lengua",	"Bajo los siguientes términos: Atribución — Usted debe dar el crédito apropiado, proporcionar un enlace a la licencia, e indicar si se hicieron cambios. Puede hacerlo de cualquier manera razonable, pero no de ninguna manera que sugiera que el licenciante lo avale a usted o a su uso. No comercial — Usted no puede utilizar el material para propósitos comerciales. No Derivatives — Si usted remezcla, transforma, o construye sobre el material, usted no puede distribuir el material modificado");
INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "支持捐款",	"你的支持可以幫助我全職拍更多好的影片，還有支持我們全家每個月的生活需要。謝謝您");
INSERT INTO posts VALUES( "Hvordan gjør du et godt kjøp, og hvordan får du mest når du skal selge bolig?", "Med lang erfaring fra hundrevis av eiendomshandler deler jeg de viktigste lærdommene mine som du vil få nytte av når du skal slå markedet! Endelig finnes det en norsk Playbook som gir deg innsidetipsene i boligmarkedet. Gjør som over 400 andre og kjøp: BOLIGKUPP OG DRØMMESALG");